WEBVTT

00:00:28.291 --> 00:00:31.000
[deru kendaraan]

00:00:48.708 --> 00:00:51.458
[deru sepeda motor]

00:01:17.083 --> 00:01:21.041
[derak ban di jalan berkerikil]

00:01:35.375 --> 00:01:38.666
[debus mesin]

00:01:48.291 --> 00:01:51.958
[gemeletap langkah]

00:02:08.333 --> 00:02:12.750
[dencing alat beradu]

00:02:15.125 --> 00:02:20.166
[deru kendaraan]

00:02:39.750 --> 00:02:42.375
[klakson kendaraan]

00:02:53.708 --> 00:02:54.666
[derak pelan]

00:03:00.041 --> 00:03:04.500
[dencing alat beradu]

00:03:15.250 --> 00:03:17.250
[pria] Kilometer berapa, ya?

00:03:17.333 --> 00:03:19.000
Kilometer 60, Bang.

00:03:19.750 --> 00:03:20.750
[berdengus]

00:03:23.541 --> 00:03:25.708
[pria] Naik dari mana Mbak ini tadi?

00:03:25.791 --> 00:03:27.833
Kilometer 26.

00:03:27.916 --> 00:03:29.375
[pria] Terus…

00:03:29.458 --> 00:03:31.166
mau turun di mana dia?

00:03:31.250 --> 00:03:32.583
[sopir truk] Ndak tahu.

00:03:32.666 --> 00:03:34.208
Dia bilang mau cari kerja.

00:03:36.541 --> 00:03:37.833
[pria] Aduh.

00:03:38.375 --> 00:03:41.166
Malam-malam begini, cari kerja di mana?

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:44.333
Yang kayak gini ini suka bawa sial.

00:03:45.125 --> 00:03:46.333
[sopir truk] Maksudnya, Bang?

00:03:47.750 --> 00:03:50.041
[pria] Ya, ini buktinya, kamu lihat.

00:03:50.125 --> 00:03:52.000
Suruh turun sini aja.

00:03:52.666 --> 00:03:54.833
Masih bagus truk ini enggak guling.

00:03:55.791 --> 00:03:57.250
Hei, kamu.

00:04:07.083 --> 00:04:08.958
Kakak mau cari kerja?

00:04:09.041 --> 00:04:10.166
Kakak ke arah sana.

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:11.583
Ya?

00:04:11.666 --> 00:04:12.875
Terus aja, jalan sana.

00:04:12.958 --> 00:04:14.583
Daerah ramai itu.

00:04:14.666 --> 00:04:16.125
Pasti banyak pekerjaan.

00:04:16.208 --> 00:04:17.333
Maaf, ya, Kak.

00:04:22.375 --> 00:04:23.708
[berdengus]

00:04:28.416 --> 00:04:31.458
[deru starter kendaraan]

00:05:30.375 --> 00:05:35.708
[musik dangdut diputar]

00:05:43.916 --> 00:05:49.541
[musik dangdut makin keras]

00:06:50.625 --> 00:06:53.083
[reporter] Gelombang demonstrasi berlanjut

00:06:53.166 --> 00:06:56.708
di tengah-tengah sidang istimewa
Majelis Permusyawaratan Rakyat.

00:06:56.791 --> 00:06:58.708
Para demonstran,
yang terdiri dari mahasiswa…

00:06:58.791 --> 00:06:59.875
[Tika] Permisi, Bu.

00:06:59.958 --> 00:07:02.375
…dan masyarakat, terus menuntut
pembersihan pemerintahan

00:07:02.458 --> 00:07:04.416
dari tokoh-tokoh Orde Baru

00:07:04.500 --> 00:07:06.625
serta penghapusan dwifungsi ABRI.

00:07:07.250 --> 00:07:10.875
Dalam pernyataannya,
Presiden Bacharuddin Jusuf Habibie

00:07:10.958 --> 00:07:13.250
meminta masyarakat
untuk mendukung pemerintahan

00:07:13.333 --> 00:07:15.791
di tengah krisis ekonomi
yang masih berlangsung…

00:07:16.416 --> 00:07:17.583
- Mau minum apa?
- …yang menyebabkan tidak stabilnya…

00:07:17.666 --> 00:07:19.083
…nilai tukar rupiah,

00:07:19.166 --> 00:07:20.958
lonjakan harta kebutuhan pokok, serta…

00:07:21.041 --> 00:07:21.875
- Hei.
- …meningkatnya…

00:07:21.958 --> 00:07:22.958
…angka pengangguran akibat…

00:07:23.041 --> 00:07:25.583
- Mau minum apa?
- Teh aja, Bu.

00:07:25.666 --> 00:07:29.625
Presiden juga menyatakan kekhawatirannya
bahwa situasi yang terus bergejolak

00:07:29.708 --> 00:07:32.375
dapat memperlambat
proses pemulihan ekonomi,

00:07:32.458 --> 00:07:36.250
yang pada akhirnya semakin memperburuk
kondisi rakyat kecil.

00:07:38.333 --> 00:07:40.791
Peningkatan pengiriman
tenaga kerja Indonesia perlu dibagi

00:07:40.875 --> 00:07:43.541
dengan ketersediaan pekerja
yang terampil dan terdidik

00:07:43.625 --> 00:07:45.625
demi terbukanya
lebih banyak kesempatan kerja

00:07:45.708 --> 00:07:47.625
dan adanya peningkatan
kesejahteraan masyarakat,

00:07:47.708 --> 00:07:50.666
serta pulihnya
stabilitas ekonomi nasional.

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:52.625
Beberapa tragedi yang terjadi belakangan,

00:07:52.708 --> 00:07:56.708
di antaranya adalah kuatnya gelombang
demonstrasi mahasiswa dan rakyat biasa

00:07:56.791 --> 00:08:00.875
yang menolak pejabat serta politisi
era Orde Baru yang masih berkuasa,

00:08:00.958 --> 00:08:02.750
serta menuntut pengadilan atas mereka,

00:08:02.833 --> 00:08:04.500
menuntut pembatasan masa jabatan presiden,

00:08:04.583 --> 00:08:07.041
dan juga perihal dwifungsi ABRI.

00:08:10.791 --> 00:08:12.500
[pelanggan pria] Cewek enggak ada
yang mampir apa, Bu?

00:08:13.708 --> 00:08:15.333
Udah pada pindah, udah lama.

00:08:15.416 --> 00:08:17.541
Lagian 'kan, juga enggak bisa karaokean.

00:08:26.833 --> 00:08:27.708
Kok buru-buru?

00:08:27.791 --> 00:08:29.041
Bosan, Bu.

00:08:29.125 --> 00:08:31.541
Pengin mangku sambil pijat-pijat enak.

00:08:31.625 --> 00:08:32.833
Sini, aku pijat-pijat.

00:08:32.916 --> 00:08:34.500
Enak juga. Mau?

00:08:34.583 --> 00:08:35.750
Kemarin ramai.

00:08:35.833 --> 00:08:36.708
[seruan dari iklan di TV]

00:08:36.791 --> 00:08:41.583
Sekarang 'kan, orangnya senangnya
nyanyi-nyanyi, karaoke, pijat-pijat.

00:08:41.666 --> 00:08:43.250
Pada stres kali.

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.083
Hei!

00:08:46.791 --> 00:08:47.916
Janan!

00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:50.125
Enggak jadi pangku-pangkuan?

00:08:50.208 --> 00:08:51.500
[pelanggan pria] Besok-besok aja!

00:08:51.583 --> 00:08:55.125
[musik ceria bermain di TV]

00:09:02.500 --> 00:09:05.666
[denging panjang]

00:09:10.583 --> 00:09:12.791
[Maya] Mau aku tutup warungnya.

00:09:16.291 --> 00:09:17.416
Hei.

00:09:38.500 --> 00:09:39.875
Mau ke mana?

00:09:45.416 --> 00:09:46.833
Tinggal di mana?

00:10:02.750 --> 00:10:04.833
Saya mau cari kerja, Bu.

00:10:04.916 --> 00:10:06.416
Apa aja.

00:10:08.541 --> 00:10:10.083
[Maya] Apa aja?

00:10:12.083 --> 00:10:13.625
Berapa bulan itu?

00:10:14.333 --> 00:10:16.000
Delapan, jalan sembilan.

00:10:21.875 --> 00:10:23.083
Mau ikut aku?

00:10:23.166 --> 00:10:24.958
[Tika bergumam setuju]

00:10:40.875 --> 00:10:42.083
[Maya] Ayo.

00:10:54.833 --> 00:10:55.833
[wanita 1] Di mana?

00:10:55.916 --> 00:10:57.000
- [wanita 2] Ini, Tante.
- Ya.

00:10:57.083 --> 00:10:57.916
- Yuk, Tante!
- Tin.

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:59.083
Hei.

00:10:59.166 --> 00:11:00.958
Masih jualan aja jam segini.

00:11:01.041 --> 00:11:03.333
Lagian, anak-anak
kalo enggak ditagihin, nunggak.

00:11:03.416 --> 00:11:04.625
Bareng, Teh?

00:11:05.541 --> 00:11:06.708
[mengemu]

00:11:06.791 --> 00:11:08.041
Temennya siapa, Bu?

00:11:08.541 --> 00:11:09.958
[musik dangdut diputar]

00:11:10.041 --> 00:11:11.750
- Siapa nama kamu?
- Tika.

00:11:11.833 --> 00:11:13.291
Sartika.

00:11:13.375 --> 00:11:15.291
[Tini] Panggil aja "Tante Tini".

00:11:15.375 --> 00:11:17.125
Kok kayaknya enggak bedakan, sih?

00:11:17.208 --> 00:11:18.833
Sayang, lah.

00:11:19.958 --> 00:11:21.708
Eh.

00:11:22.333 --> 00:11:25.041
Tapi saya punya jamu-jamu
bekal kandungan. Ada.

00:11:25.125 --> 00:11:27.083
Bawa, sih. Nanti dibawain. Mau? Mau, ya?

00:11:27.166 --> 00:11:29.083
- Ayo, ah. Ayo.
- Bayarnya boleh nyicil. Harian boleh.

00:11:29.166 --> 00:11:32.375
Kamu jualan jam lima.
Ini juga belum sampai rumah, Tin.

00:11:32.458 --> 00:11:34.708
Belum selesai ngomong.
Dipotong aja, Bu Maya.

00:11:34.791 --> 00:11:36.916
Itu rencananya kapan berojolnya?
Kabarin, ya, Bu.

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.833
- Bu. [berdecak]
- [Maya] Ya.

00:11:49.083 --> 00:11:52.875
[jangkrik mengerik]

00:12:03.833 --> 00:12:04.833
Ayo masuk.

00:12:13.791 --> 00:12:15.083
Pak.

00:12:16.041 --> 00:12:18.708
Pak. Bangun, Pak.

00:12:18.791 --> 00:12:20.333
Pindah ke sana, Pak.

00:12:27.458 --> 00:12:29.250
Kamu sini aja.

00:12:40.958 --> 00:12:43.041
Enggak usah khawatir.

00:12:43.125 --> 00:12:45.791
Udah tua, udah enggak bisa apa-apa.

00:12:49.291 --> 00:12:51.000
Kamu tidur aja.

00:12:57.125 --> 00:12:58.583
[Tika] Bu.

00:12:58.666 --> 00:13:00.083
Makasih, ya, Bu.

00:13:03.958 --> 00:13:09.208
[musik lembut mengalun]

00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:23.666
[Maya] Dulu kerja apa?

00:14:25.583 --> 00:14:28.000
[Tika] Saya dulu cuci, setrika,

00:14:28.083 --> 00:14:31.416
sama, ya, apa ajalah, Bu,
yang bisa dikerjain.

00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:39.500
[Maya] Orang tua di mana?

00:14:40.083 --> 00:14:41.625
[Tika] Ada di kampung.

00:14:42.166 --> 00:14:45.875
Tapi sisa Ibu.
Kalo Bapak, udah enggak ada.

00:14:48.625 --> 00:14:50.500
[Maya] Kamu pergi dari rumah?

00:14:51.291 --> 00:14:52.625
Apa diusir?

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:04.416
Kalau mau kerja di warung,

00:15:05.041 --> 00:15:08.625
cuma bikin kopi, duduk-duduk,

00:15:08.708 --> 00:15:10.125
gampang, 'kan?

00:15:13.416 --> 00:15:15.708
Dan enggak banyak juga yang datang.

00:15:17.833 --> 00:15:22.250
Siapa tau, kalau ada kamu, tambah ramai.

00:15:24.333 --> 00:15:31.208
Tapi kalo kerja di warung, mesti ngelendot
sambil dipangku-pangku gitu, Bu?

00:15:31.291 --> 00:15:33.541
Enggak ada yang paksa.

00:15:33.625 --> 00:15:37.791
Lagian, orang hamil kayak gini,
orang juga mikir kali.

00:15:41.708 --> 00:15:43.041
[mengesah]

00:15:51.083 --> 00:15:55.375
Emang kalo enggak di sini,
kamu tau mau ke mana?

00:16:01.791 --> 00:16:05.083
Katanya mau kerja apa aja.

00:16:05.166 --> 00:16:07.000
Mau jadi TKW?

00:16:08.458 --> 00:16:11.000
Dengar-dengar banyak yang disiksa.

00:16:14.958 --> 00:16:17.083
Kalo Bapak, kerjanya apa, Bu?

00:16:17.166 --> 00:16:18.625
[anak-anak berbicara samar]

00:16:18.708 --> 00:16:21.291
Dulu buruh pabrik plastik.

00:16:22.083 --> 00:16:25.083
Sekarang kadang kerja di sawah.

00:16:27.541 --> 00:16:30.416
Berarti bisa, ya, Bu, kerja di pabrik?

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:32.791
Pabrik udah banyak yang tutup.

00:16:33.416 --> 00:16:36.291
Lagi krismon gini susah cari kerja.

00:16:42.875 --> 00:16:48.708
[musik lembut mengalun]

00:16:53.750 --> 00:16:57.208
[deru kapal]

00:17:08.208 --> 00:17:14.166
- [Tini] Ayo. He-eh, gitu. Ayo, kuat.
- [Maya] Napas dalam. Ayo.

00:17:14.250 --> 00:17:18.166
- [Tika mengejan]
- [Maya] Dorong. Dorong keluar. Terus.

00:17:18.250 --> 00:17:24.458
- Jangan ditahan. Dorong kuat. Ayo, bisa.
- [Tini] Ayo. Semangat. Ayo, keluar!

00:17:24.541 --> 00:17:26.958
- [Maya] Ayo.
- [Tini] Enggak ada lap bersih, Bu?

00:17:27.041 --> 00:17:28.250
[bayi menangis]

00:17:28.333 --> 00:17:30.458
[Maya] Wah.

00:17:30.541 --> 00:17:33.583
[Tini] Alhamdulillah, ya Allah.

00:17:34.208 --> 00:17:36.375
Aduh.

00:17:37.125 --> 00:17:42.666
[tikus mendecit]

00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:03.166
Coba kasih ini.

00:18:06.791 --> 00:18:07.875
[berdeham]

00:18:13.625 --> 00:18:15.333
Ini. Ya.

00:18:19.500 --> 00:18:21.208
[mengemu gemas]

00:18:22.041 --> 00:18:23.083
Lagi?

00:18:23.666 --> 00:18:24.833
Enak?

00:18:26.833 --> 00:18:28.041
Sut.

00:18:28.750 --> 00:18:30.000
Udah.

00:18:33.875 --> 00:18:36.041
Ah?

00:18:39.375 --> 00:18:41.791
[tertawa]

00:18:43.708 --> 00:18:44.875
Enak?

00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:49.125
Enak, ya?

00:18:50.833 --> 00:18:52.041
Enak, ya? Ya?

00:18:59.166 --> 00:19:00.750
[mengesah]

00:19:05.250 --> 00:19:07.916
[berdengus]

00:19:10.375 --> 00:19:14.125
[bayi menangis]

00:19:21.041 --> 00:19:25.000
[bayi menangis]

00:19:55.250 --> 00:19:56.416
- Makasih.
- Ya.

00:19:59.333 --> 00:20:00.541
Ya.

00:20:02.750 --> 00:20:05.875
[bayi menangis]

00:20:26.958 --> 00:20:30.250
[bayi menangis]

00:20:44.791 --> 00:20:47.166
Sut…

00:20:48.708 --> 00:20:50.916
[bayi berceloteh]

00:21:03.416 --> 00:21:04.791
[bayi menangis]

00:21:35.333 --> 00:21:36.458
[Tika] Bu.

00:21:38.666 --> 00:21:40.916
[deru kendaraan]

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:46.500
[musik sendu mengalun]

00:21:49.541 --> 00:21:52.250
[bayi berceloteh]

00:21:57.458 --> 00:21:59.666
[ayam berkokok]

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:11.583
[bayi berceloteh]

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:25.541
[berceloteh lembut]

00:22:35.125 --> 00:22:37.750
[mengesah]

00:22:41.500 --> 00:22:46.166
[musik gitar pelan mengalun]

00:23:07.291 --> 00:23:09.166
[reporter] Sebagai upaya
pemulihan ekonomi Indonesia

00:23:09.250 --> 00:23:10.708
pascakrisis moneter,

00:23:10.791 --> 00:23:13.333
Presiden Bacharuddin Jusuf Habibie

00:23:13.416 --> 00:23:17.375
membentuk BKPTKI

00:23:17.458 --> 00:23:20.666
yang berhak menjawab langsung
kepada presiden

00:23:20.750 --> 00:23:25.208
berdasarkan Keputusan Presiden
Nomor 20 Tahun 1999.

00:23:25.291 --> 00:23:28.958
BKPTKI bertugas membantu presiden
dalam meningkatkan program

00:23:29.041 --> 00:23:31.875
dan penempatan pekerja Indonesia

00:23:31.958 --> 00:23:35.500
dengan memperhatikan kualitas
dan keamanan ketepatan tenaga kerja,

00:23:35.583 --> 00:23:39.625
serta penyediaan pemasaran
dan perlindungannya di luar negeri.

00:23:40.291 --> 00:23:45.250
Peningkatan pengiriman tenaga kerja
Indonesia telah menjadi bagian…

00:24:27.458 --> 00:24:28.625
Hati-hati, panas.

00:24:28.708 --> 00:24:29.833
[mengemu]

00:24:33.875 --> 00:24:36.125
[menyesap]

00:24:36.208 --> 00:24:37.541
Manis, enggak?

00:24:37.625 --> 00:24:38.541
Wah… [berdecak]

00:24:39.500 --> 00:24:42.291
Duduk di sini, sih.
Jadi manis nih kopinya.

00:24:42.375 --> 00:24:43.666
Bisa aja.

00:24:55.541 --> 00:24:57.416
Entar beliin aku rokok, dong.

00:24:59.958 --> 00:25:00.875
Mau rokok apa?

00:25:00.958 --> 00:25:02.541
Yang di situ, tuh.

00:25:03.500 --> 00:25:04.500
Ya?

00:25:05.125 --> 00:25:06.166
Beliin, enggak?

00:25:06.708 --> 00:25:07.708
Boleh.

00:25:07.791 --> 00:25:09.166
[Bayu] Bu…

00:25:09.250 --> 00:25:12.458
- Ibu…
- Ibu lagi bikin kopi. Ya?

00:25:14.125 --> 00:25:16.125
Bayu sama Mbok aja, ya?

00:25:16.208 --> 00:25:18.000
[Maya] Ya? He-em?

00:25:18.083 --> 00:25:19.916
Mau sama Mbok? Udah.

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.041
Enak, 'kan?

00:25:25.125 --> 00:25:27.083
[percakapan samar]

00:25:34.583 --> 00:25:36.541
[pria 1 berbahasa Jawa]
Delapan. Empat delapan, empat sama…

00:25:36.625 --> 00:25:38.541
[pria 2 berbahasa Indonesia]
Cuma jual empat…

00:25:40.625 --> 00:25:42.375
[pria 3] Tujuh belas rupiah.

00:25:42.458 --> 00:25:44.916
[pria 3 berbicara samar]

00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:47.541
[gerantang]

00:25:57.458 --> 00:25:58.458
Izin, Kang.

00:25:59.708 --> 00:26:00.791
Izin berapa lama?

00:26:00.875 --> 00:26:02.041
Seminggu, Kang.

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:04.208
Acara apaan?

00:26:04.833 --> 00:26:06.916
Antar istri, mau ke Saudi.

00:26:08.250 --> 00:26:10.916
Kok orang-orang yang istrinya
mau jadi TKW izinnya sampai seminggu?

00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:13.083
'Kan, mampir kampung dulu, Kang,

00:26:13.166 --> 00:26:14.541
[percakapan samar]

00:26:15.333 --> 00:26:16.416
Makasih, Kang.

00:26:49.833 --> 00:26:51.208
Berapa titik nanti?

00:26:51.708 --> 00:26:53.083
Paling tiga, Mas.

00:26:53.583 --> 00:26:55.750
Habis itu, mampir bisa, lah.

00:27:02.958 --> 00:27:04.708
- Kamu kopi aja?
- He-em.

00:27:08.375 --> 00:27:09.375
Bu.

00:27:09.458 --> 00:27:11.291
Kopi dua, kacang satu.

00:27:12.666 --> 00:27:13.541
Makasih, Bu.

00:27:14.125 --> 00:27:15.083
Yuk, Bu.

00:27:15.166 --> 00:27:16.541
[wanita berbicara samar]

00:27:22.708 --> 00:27:23.750
[duk pelan]

00:27:25.166 --> 00:27:29.166
Saya kasih tau berapa kali
kalo ngitung yang benar?

00:27:29.250 --> 00:27:30.166
Ha?

00:27:31.000 --> 00:27:33.208
- Tau, enggak, ini masalahnya duit?
- Maaf.

00:27:34.250 --> 00:27:36.333
Lu salah angkut, mau nanggung duitnya?

00:27:37.583 --> 00:27:38.875
