Sehat-sehat.

01:18:09.916 --> 01:18:11.333
- [mengesah]
- [berdesit]

01:18:16.541 --> 01:18:17.750
[berdesit]

01:18:20.166 --> 01:18:21.333
[mengesah]

01:18:26.750 --> 01:18:29.458
Pengantin baru yang senang.

01:18:45.125 --> 01:18:47.416
Ngapain, sih, bikin layangan lagi?

01:18:47.500 --> 01:18:49.625
Bapakmu 'kan, bisa beli yang banyak.

01:18:50.500 --> 01:18:52.291
Bapak udah lama enggak pulang.

01:18:53.125 --> 01:18:55.208
Kulihat Ibu sering nangis.

01:18:56.000 --> 01:18:58.083
Sibuk kali di tempat anjing.

01:18:59.291 --> 01:19:00.750
Anjing siapa?

01:19:00.833 --> 01:19:02.208
Anjing gondrong.

01:19:02.875 --> 01:19:05.625
[berdengus] Emangnya ada anjing
yang gondrong?

01:19:07.666 --> 01:19:09.541
Layangan yang kemarin aku bikin ke mana?

01:19:09.625 --> 01:19:11.291
Dibeli teman di sekolah.

01:19:12.000 --> 01:19:14.291
Katanya bagus. Enggak gampang sobek.

01:19:15.166 --> 01:19:16.333
Dibeli berapa?

01:19:22.166 --> 01:19:23.166
Ha?

01:19:27.458 --> 01:19:28.583
Bagi dua, ya?

01:19:30.333 --> 01:19:34.000
Tadi malam si Yuna bilang
udah lama enggak ketemu si Asep.

01:19:34.666 --> 01:19:38.458
Terakhir kali ketemu Asep, katanya dia
udah enggak kerja lagi sama suami kamu.

01:19:40.375 --> 01:19:41.458
[mengesah]

01:19:49.250 --> 01:19:53.166
Makanya, kalo lagi suntuk di rumah,
sering-sering ke sini.

01:19:54.541 --> 01:19:58.625
Orang laki, kalo lagi kerja biarin aja,
yang penting duit masuk.

01:20:05.625 --> 01:20:07.791
Daripada ada laki,
tapi enggak ngasih duit?

01:20:08.500 --> 01:20:09.541
Yuk.

01:20:09.625 --> 01:20:10.583
[berdesit]

01:20:16.000 --> 01:20:18.583
Semenjak enggak ada kamu, warung sepi.

01:20:21.083 --> 01:20:24.208
Anak-anak setan itu
paling sekali-sekali datang,

01:20:25.625 --> 01:20:27.541
kalo butuh kamar.

01:20:27.625 --> 01:20:28.916
Maaf, ya, Bu.

01:20:34.958 --> 01:20:36.875
Enggak usah minta maaf.

01:20:48.125 --> 01:20:50.666
Tuh gerobak mi bagaimana? Udah jadi?

01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:01.791
Udah, enggak usah banyak mikir.

01:21:09.291 --> 01:21:11.041
Jalanin aja, Tik.

01:21:30.708 --> 01:21:31.750
Awas.

01:21:32.916 --> 01:21:33.875
[berseru]

01:21:41.083 --> 01:21:42.166
[Bayu] Sana.

01:21:42.875 --> 01:21:43.833
[Gilang] Tarik, ya.

01:21:44.833 --> 01:21:46.291
[Bayu] Mundur…

01:21:46.375 --> 01:21:47.541
Mundur! Stop!

01:21:48.208 --> 01:21:49.125
Stop!

01:21:49.208 --> 01:21:50.541
[Gilang] Oke. Tarik!

01:21:50.625 --> 01:21:52.375
- Satu…
- [Bayu] Satu, dua, tiga!

01:22:15.166 --> 01:22:16.333
Bu.

01:22:17.291 --> 01:22:18.458
Bangun, Bu.

01:22:19.208 --> 01:22:20.416
Makan.

01:22:29.916 --> 01:22:30.958
Bu?

01:22:32.375 --> 01:22:33.458
- Bu.
- Hmm?

01:22:33.541 --> 01:22:34.625
Makan.

01:22:35.250 --> 01:22:36.916
- Hmm?
- Makan dulu.

01:22:38.750 --> 01:22:40.916
Makanan dari mana itu?

01:22:45.083 --> 01:22:47.250
Itu… Bapak pulang, ya?

01:22:48.541 --> 01:22:50.875
Layangannya banyak yang beli.

01:22:51.958 --> 01:22:54.166
Ibu masih sakit?

01:22:54.250 --> 01:22:56.375
Ibu enggak usah kerja dulu.

01:22:56.458 --> 01:22:57.458
Ini masih ada uang.

01:22:57.541 --> 01:22:58.416
[tertawa pelan]

01:22:58.500 --> 01:23:00.375
Enggak, Ibu enggak sakit, kok.

01:23:01.000 --> 01:23:03.083
Tapi simpan aja uangnya.

01:23:03.166 --> 01:23:05.166
Entar juga Ibu bisa kerja.

01:23:06.083 --> 01:23:07.750
Mau jualan mi ayam, 'kan, kita?

01:23:07.833 --> 01:23:08.791
- Iya.
- [bergumam]

01:23:08.875 --> 01:23:10.041
Bu.

01:23:10.125 --> 01:23:13.833
Masa tadi kata Kak Gilang,
Bapak ada di tempat anjing,

01:23:13.916 --> 01:23:15.708
terus anjingnya gondrong.

01:23:16.333 --> 01:23:18.458
Masa anjingnya gondrong?

01:23:21.708 --> 01:23:23.125
[deru sepeda motor]

01:23:42.750 --> 01:23:44.500
Di sebelah mananya?

01:23:45.333 --> 01:23:50.625
Nanti Mbak Tika lurus aja,
masuk ke pintu, naik tangga.

01:23:50.708 --> 01:23:52.958
Nanti orangnya gede, botak.

01:23:53.041 --> 01:23:54.583
Katanya gondrong?

01:23:55.666 --> 01:23:57.166
Nanti Mbak lihat sendiri aja.

01:23:57.833 --> 01:24:01.583
[dentang berulang dari kejauhan]

01:24:07.000 --> 01:24:09.625
[pria berbicara samar]

01:24:58.458 --> 01:25:02.458
[percakapan tanpa suara]

01:25:08.291 --> 01:25:12.958
[musik sedih mengalun]

01:25:36.875 --> 01:25:38.416
[deru sepeda motor]

01:25:43.000 --> 01:25:46.125
Yuk. Ke rumah Ibu.

01:25:46.208 --> 01:25:48.041
[terisak] Rumah Ibu…

01:26:09.916 --> 01:26:12.583
Enggak usah dipikirin, Tik.

01:26:15.416 --> 01:26:18.333
Kamu bisa pulang kapan pun kamu mau.

01:26:21.000 --> 01:26:23.291
Ini 'kan, rumah kamu juga.

01:26:27.791 --> 01:26:28.791
Udah.

01:27:23.333 --> 01:27:24.166
[ketuk berulang]

01:27:26.333 --> 01:27:27.416
Bu.

01:27:27.500 --> 01:27:29.750
[Bayu] Ada temannya, Bu.

01:27:34.750 --> 01:27:36.000
[wanita] Sartika?

01:27:38.666 --> 01:27:41.458
Saya Anissa. Saya…

01:27:42.375 --> 01:27:44.208
Ya, saya tau siapa Mbak.

01:27:46.000 --> 01:27:47.500
Silakan masuk.

01:28:13.291 --> 01:28:17.083
Bajingan itu menghabiskan uang
yang saya kirim dari Arab Saudi.

01:28:23.250 --> 01:28:25.625
Capek, lho, saya kerja bertahun-tahun.

01:28:28.750 --> 01:28:30.958
Tapi cuman ini hasilnya?

01:28:34.000 --> 01:28:37.708
Saya pikir kalian punya rumah
yang lebih bagus dari ini.

01:29:06.958 --> 01:29:08.083
[derak pintu dibuka]

01:29:14.500 --> 01:29:15.833
[terengah-engah]

01:29:19.458 --> 01:29:20.583
Bayu.

01:29:23.333 --> 01:29:24.333
Bayu.

01:29:30.958 --> 01:29:32.125
Pakai itu.

01:29:33.666 --> 01:29:35.125
Kita mau ke mana, Bu?

01:29:35.208 --> 01:29:36.500
Udah, pakai.

01:29:36.583 --> 01:29:37.583
Pakai.

01:29:37.666 --> 01:29:39.833
[terisak] Pakai sendiri.
Masa enggak bisa, sih?

01:29:41.500 --> 01:29:43.208
- Kita mau ke mana, Bu?
- Udah, pakai.

01:29:52.833 --> 01:29:53.875
Masukin.

01:30:01.250 --> 01:30:03.875
[debak-debuk barang dimasukkan]

01:30:08.916 --> 01:30:10.833
[kelentang]

01:30:10.916 --> 01:30:11.875
[Tika] Udah.

01:30:14.791 --> 01:30:17.083
Bapak! Bapak, Bu!

01:30:17.833 --> 01:30:19.958
- Bapak!
- Bayu!

01:30:20.041 --> 01:30:21.750
- Sartika.
- Bapak!

01:30:23.875 --> 01:30:25.791
Bawa sampah itu.
Saya enggak mau lihat di situ.

01:30:25.875 --> 01:30:26.916
[Bayu] Bapak.

01:30:27.000 --> 01:30:28.125
Kenapa Bapak…

01:30:28.208 --> 01:30:29.958
Bapak, kangen.

01:30:30.041 --> 01:30:32.000
- [Hadi] Maafin Bapak.
- [Bayu merajuk]

01:30:32.875 --> 01:30:33.916
[Hadi] Bapak…

01:30:34.625 --> 01:30:36.041
[Bayu] Bapak…

01:30:36.750 --> 01:30:38.083
[Bayu merajuk]

01:30:38.166 --> 01:30:40.041
Bayu jagain Ibu, ya?

01:30:45.500 --> 01:30:47.375
[Bayu berbicara samar]

01:30:47.458 --> 01:30:49.041
[Hadi] Maafin Bapak.

01:30:50.791 --> 01:30:53.208
[terisak pelan]

01:30:57.416 --> 01:30:59.916
[Bayu] Bapak…

01:31:05.583 --> 01:31:06.666
Pak?

01:31:19.458 --> 01:31:21.500
Bayu, ikut Ibu. [mengerang]

01:31:21.583 --> 01:31:23.375
[terisak] Udah, ikut Ibu!

01:31:30.916 --> 01:31:33.208
[menangis]

01:31:33.291 --> 01:31:34.875
Bapak…

01:31:36.500 --> 01:31:37.666
[terisak]

01:31:55.083 --> 01:32:00.958
[musik sendu mengalun]

01:32:13.291 --> 01:32:14.125
[Sita berdecak]

01:32:14.208 --> 01:32:19.500
Laki tuh emang, ya.
"Itu"-nya doang yang bisa dipegang.

01:32:20.291 --> 01:32:21.333
Omongannya, sih, enggak.

01:32:21.416 --> 01:32:22.916
[Tika menangis]

01:32:24.250 --> 01:32:26.916
Makanya, aku enggak percaya
cinta-cintaan, Tik.

01:32:28.916 --> 01:32:31.625
Kamar aja, udah. Selesai.

01:32:33.750 --> 01:32:36.000
[Yuna] Tapi itu 'kan, kamu, Sit.

01:32:37.125 --> 01:32:39.708
Tika itu udah enggak punya apa-apa.

01:32:40.375 --> 01:32:44.750
Jadi, kalau cinta dateng,
ya, masa kita enggak mau?

01:33:13.250 --> 01:33:18.041
[musik lembut mengalun]

01:34:19.458 --> 01:34:20.333
[Bayu] Bu.

01:34:20.958 --> 01:34:22.416
Gerobaknya di sana?

01:34:39.625 --> 01:34:40.625
Pak…

01:34:56.041 --> 01:34:57.125
[Maya] Ayo bobo.

01:34:58.916 --> 01:35:01.083
Eh, copot dulu sandalnya.

01:35:58.208 --> 01:35:59.875
Sekar, ayo.

01:36:05.208 --> 01:36:07.666
Bu, Sekar berangkat, ya.

01:36:07.750 --> 01:36:10.583
[decur air]

01:36:28.041 --> 01:36:29.500
Bu, pamit, ya!

01:37:31.750 --> 01:37:36.708
["Ibu" oleh Iwan Fals mengalun]

01:37:44.875 --> 01:37:45.833
[Bayu Kecil] Bu.

01:37:45.916 --> 01:37:49.041
Hari ini, Ibu enggak usah
jualan dulu, ya, Bu.

01:37:50.416 --> 01:37:53.625
Bayu mungkin belum bisa kasih Ibu apa-apa,

01:37:54.416 --> 01:37:57.250
tapi aku mau bilang terima kasih,

01:37:57.333 --> 01:38:00.958
Ibu sudah memilih
melahirkan Bayu dan Sekar,

01:38:01.041 --> 01:38:03.208
dan bekerja buat kami.

01:38:04.458 --> 01:38:08.333
[percakapan tanpa suara]

01:38:08.416 --> 01:38:12.916
Mbok dan Kakek pasti bangga
lihat Ibu dari atas sana.

01:38:15.250 --> 01:38:19.000
Ini ada sedikit uang tabungan Bayu
buat Ibu.

01:38:20.083 --> 01:38:22.500
Ibu beli apa yang Ibu mau.

01:38:23.250 --> 01:38:26.541
Jangan lupa, nanti Bayu pulang,
kita makan enak.

01:38:29.458 --> 01:38:31.916
Bayu dan Sekar bangga punya Ibu.

01:38:34.166 --> 01:38:36.083
Selamat ulang tahun, Ibu.

